## Romantic and Vintage Rose Gold Pear Diamond Settings

Rose gold's Art Nouveau and early 20th-century associations make it the natural metal for romantic and vintage-inspired pear ring designs. Unlike yellow gold — which anchors to Victorian-Edwardian history — rose gold is associated with a softer, more decorative ornamental tradition.

